I don’t know why in a restaurant and during a global pandemic on top of all things a staff member would be preparing orders without a mask and gloves on, he then proceeded to wiping his hands covered in bbq sauce with a rag that was already dirty and had the audacity to use that same rag to wipe the counter top, that was completely disgusting and disturbing. A side from that, I arrived at the restaurant in about 30min but my Order wasn’t ready and at that point was when they started to prepare it, mind you I was given an estimate that my order would be ready in about 23min and it took them about 40min to prepare it, I was there waiting and watching other customers who came after me with larger orders receiving theirs while I just patiently waited, unacceptable. To make matters worse the staffs customers service was the worse I’ve ever seen, it’ll be an understatement to call it awful or horrendous. No one even bothered to apologize or acknowledge what just happened. For these reasons honestly speaking I will never go back to that specific restaurant again. I have also informed my family and friends of this ordeal and they were also deeply disgusted and will never step foot in that establishment. It is extremely sad that this occurred because I love wing stop and have never had anything bad to say until now, my only hope is that someone from upper management reads this and rectifies these issues so other future customers could have a way better experience than I did.
